Nothing gets past you, huh Yanshosh?

* There was just no escaping him was there? She was easily outdistencing 
him...until she looked back and saw Prowl transform into beast mode.
She growled, oh great! Now she bet he was going to try and stop her now.
Even thought she knew that he was worried and it was very sweet, she still 
wanted to find out just what had happened to her too.
And with that, she changed course a bit and started heading for the forest 
at the far end of the plain. Knowing that it could take her all the way to 
the Ark, and if Prowl lost her in there then maybe he would go back to base 
and stay there like she had ordered.
But she growled.*

" I told you to stay back at base, now go!!"

* Basically calling over her shoulder.*
